            "title": "盤中速報 - 超豐(2441)股價拉至漲停，漲停價105.5元，成交15,007張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>超豐(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2441:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2441\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2441-TW</a>)16日10:07上漲9.3元，股價漲停報105.5元，委買4張、委賣1,428張，成交15,007張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為各種積體電路之封裝、測試及相關業務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>超豐(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2441:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2441\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2441-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲9.82%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.48%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,140 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+240 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+110 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+790 張</li> <li>融資增減：+2,051 張</li> <li>融券增減：+1,006 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
